Package com.snamp.connectors

Represents SNAMP connector architectural layer.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AttributeJavaTypeInfo<T>
    Represents mapping between MIB( management information base) specific type system and native JVM type system
    AttributeMetadata
    Represents attribute metadata,
    AttributeTabularType
    Represents a table type of the attribute value.
    AttributeTypeInfo
    Represents an information about attribute type.
    AttributeTypeInfoBuilder.AttributeConvertibleTypeInfo<T>
    Represents advanced representation of the AttributeTypeInfoBuilder.AttributeConvertibleTypeInfo that supports conversion methods.
    ManagementConnector
    Represents management connector that exposes management attributes of the remote provider.
    ManagementConnectorFactory
    Represents management connector factory.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractManagementConnector
    Represents an abstract class for building custom management connectors.
    AbstractManagementConnector.GenericAttributeMetadata<T extends AttributeTypeInfo>
    Represents default implementation of the attribute descriptor.
    AbstractManagementConnectorFactory<TConnector extends ManagementConnector>
    Represents a base class for building management connectors.
    Arguments
    Represents action invocation arguments,
    AttributeArrayType
    Represents single-dimensional array type as table.
    AttributePrimitiveTypeBuilder
    Represents builder for primitive types.
    AttributeTypeInfoBuilder
    Represents builder for AttributeTypeInfo instances.
    ManagementConnectorBean
    Represents SNAMP in-process management connector that exposes Java Bean properties through connector attributes.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    AttributeTypeInfoBuilder.Converter
    Marks the method with single argument and non-void return value as converter.
